                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780715-66-off324 t17780715-66-crimeloc327"></join>; I lost the things mentioned in the indictment out of my chamber; I saw them about twelve at noon and missed them about four; the prisoner sold them to a woman.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-66-person611">
                  ANNE
                   ADLAM
               <interp inst="t17780715-66-person611" type="surname" value="ADLAM"></interp>
