                     <interp inst="t17780715-66-person611" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner came to my house in Bennet's court, Drury-lane, on Midsummer-day, at about six in the afternoon, and sold me these buckles; I gave him twelve shillings and sixpence for them, and he gave me a receipt.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-66-person612">
